No. 10-1519. Florida, Petitioner v. David Lamar Garland. 565 U.S. 1045, 132 S. Ct. 574,

181 L. Ed. 2d 441,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8125. November 14, 2011.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the District Court of Appeal of Florida, First District, denied.

Same case below, 70 So. 3d 609.
